Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years have passed\Nsince the Paramount War at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew\Neach completed individual training,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and on their way\Nto the next stage, the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they reached Fishman Island,\Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there they found\Nthe New Fishman Pirates disturbing the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah?! You're a huge lady... I mean, Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Father-sama! Brother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa! I didn't do anything to you, did I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, damn! What's with you?!
