Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.02,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,It's no time for playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wadatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get a reply yet?\NA reply from Princess Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet, Captain Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have I been waiting for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For ten years or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of that hateful Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to force Princess Shirahoshi\Ninto a political marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is, the Princess has been locked up\Nin the steel tower for ten whole years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how painful this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we love each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.81,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,I suspect!
