Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:08.62,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I roam this vast seafloor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find someone who is as great\Nand beautiful as you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we end up together, then all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I cannot allow you to live with another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather see you dead\Nthan with somebody else, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either "Death or Marriage" for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, let me present you with a rose-emblazoned axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As proof of our marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain? It's way off target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! I don't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading towards Ryugu Palace!
