Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, whoa! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a pirate who came here looking for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's loud! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi-sama's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from Hard Shell Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the tower guards doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why is nobody with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! The guard shifts were changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, get to the tower now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A human is... here in the room... trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No! Hey! That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hungry and I didn't know the food was yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that axe?!\NWhere'd it come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.81,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(455,500,\1a&H00&)}Ryugu Palace, Main Entrance
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.81,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Ryugu Palace, Main Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.81,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the banquet happening? How long do we have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach is growling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have a stomach that could growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we're having a banquet any time soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean that we've landed ourselves in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that you came all the way here\Nbut we've just received a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You Straw Hat people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are suspects in two ongoing investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Suspects?! What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First, for multiple counts of Mermaid kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't do—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, you people are suspected\Nof being potential risks to Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,according to Madame Sharley's future vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Future vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know if that'll happen for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we're here\Nto take you people into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch them at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to protect Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.04,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying louder\Nthan usual—we were worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who opened this door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry to make you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I had a bad dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I heard somebody for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's... Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach made a noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo! Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes! There is something I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Straw Hat Luffy, the pirate who saved Megalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a suspect in the kidnapping of some missing Mermaid girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And due to Madame Sharley's prediction,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the Straw Hats are considered an unconfirmed but potential risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so we've decided to lock them\Nin the palace prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We took the swordsman, who arrived first,\Ninto custody after he fell asleep from drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The three members who just arrived are probably in custody by now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But their captain—Straw Hat—who was with them,\Nmight have noticed our intentions and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He is probably hiding somewhere in the palace so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll catch the rest that're on the island and defend this country at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you? Wasn't it just your imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad we have to arrest\Nthe people who saved Megalo's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama, you're acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Right, we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's been five minutes already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock the doors tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being very rude to you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that you were the one\Nwho saved Megalo's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,May I call you Luffy-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, you're a pirate;\Ndoes that mean you're also a bad person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. You decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they said that our soldiers took your friends into custody...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can't keep them under control anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell me, what's with that axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who threw it? From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Vander Decken-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He holds a grudge against me for refusing to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That man has attained the Devil's power\Nthrough the Mark-Mark curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He can strike me anytime, anywhere, since he's designated me as his mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's too dangerous for me\Nto leave Hard Shell Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum-yum! Can I eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to marry you but he's trying to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ten years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years?! You must be bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:15:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, my father made a rule\Nthat soldiers can't stay here more than five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Megalo is the only one I can talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why they wanted to hold a banquet for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's canceled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they want to put Megalo's liberators in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Madame Sharley-sama's future visions\Nare unbelievably accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains why everyone's afraid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you humans eat a lot\Neven though you're so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That hairy old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,said we were gonna have a banquet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but he kept getting scolded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I couldn't wait any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I followed the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did they call you Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the Mermaid Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am King Neptune's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. That's hard to pronounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna eat that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're such a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you seek adventures since you're a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Have you ever seen the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are stars in the night sky, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are different kinds of flowers and hairy animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been\Nto a green place called a "forest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wait, wait! That's too many questions! Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a big cheek pouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,P-P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't yell at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama is a scary man just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa! I didn't do anything\Nto make you cry! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never been yelled at by anyone before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be big but you're a coward and a crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No one ever said such a horrible thing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm full! Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been here for ten years, huh?\NThat would probably make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, please leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't there anywhere you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a lot of places I want to go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No, I'm not supposed to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If something's thrown at you again, I'll deflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy! How can he sleep under these circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}did{\i0} drink like crazy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Things sure are getting busy in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-chin! Nami-chin! Brook-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just three humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! If you resist any more,\Nyou're really gonna become criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no reason for us\Nto obey them, Camie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking forward to a banquet at Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll just arrest us if we don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They made unthinkable accusations against us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take on as many of you\Nas you like, if you so desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so strong even without the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we might do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't arrest us now\Nfor things we haven't even done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The nose guy wasn't ever\Nthat dependable, was he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook-chin and Nami-chin have gotten a lot tougher\Nthan they were two years ago, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's the prologue to the future\Nthat has been predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! If you guys didn't start this,\Nwe wouldn't have to fight back in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is nothing compared to the giant insects'\Nall-out attack on Bowin Islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness the power of my new weapon—Black Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama, we need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's fair to arrest somebody\Nbased on a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some time to think-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to be in custody for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's formidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the sounds of a festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so I let myself out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.86,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Captain Decken, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.47,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Wait there, Wadatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:25.07,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(480,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(435,480,\1a&H00&)}Fishman District, Noah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.86,0:21:25.07,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(480,0)\4a&HFF&}Fishman District, Noah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.07,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Decken-sama is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran into a volcanic eruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the notorious Hody?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're notorious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nutty Vander Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a handshake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're unbeatable on the seafloor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst of the worst coming together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:35.64,Alt,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody! Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.67,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hody! Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody! Hody!
