Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody! Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:45.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hody! Hody!
