Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:47.32,Alt,,0,0,0,,Decken! Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune is a nuisance for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:23:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat the Neptune Army who take no pride\Nin being Fishmen or Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And kill Neptune, the God of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We will destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Kingdom completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:12.71,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Kingdom completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats are facing\Nthe God of the Sea, Neptune's, army.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Neptune's soldiers attempt to break the bubbles\Nprotecting Zoro's group to turn the tables of the battle.
